file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: API
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
   '/':
    get:
      parameters:
      - $ref: '#/components/parameters/c'
      responses:
        default:
          description: OK
components:
  schemas:
    a:
      allOf:
      - $ref: '#/components/schemas/b'
      - description: a
    b:
      type: integer
  parameters:
    c:
      name: c
      in: query
      schema:
        type: string
